  "title": "Uncaught Error: Minified exception occurred; use the non-minified dev environment for the full error message and additional helpful warnings.",
  "body": "I've disabled all of our other javascript, so we are just using the instantsearch.js code as in the examples.  No matter what I do (search, click a page, etc) I am always getting this error.    This error is coming from the invariant.js script.   Unsure if this is just a configuration issue or what.   Just trying to do a pretty basic setup with a search box, hits container, and pagination.\n\nShould mention that the initial render works fine, it's populating the first page of results as it should.  Just can't do anything from there.\n",
